longBusinessSummary: PT Gudang Garam Tbk produces and sells cigarettes in Indonesia and internationally. The company operates through Cigarettes, Paperboards, and Others segments. It offers hand-rolled, machine-made, and klobot clove cigarettes. The company markets its products under the Gudang Garam Family, Surya Family, GG Family, and other brand names. It is also involved in trading activities; and provision of safety protective equipment, and investment and construction services. In addition, the company provides tobacco processing, non-scheduled air transportation, and entertainment services. The company was formerly known as PT Perusahaan Rokok Tjap Gudang Garam Kediri. PT Gudang Garam Tbk was founded in 1958 and is headquartered in Kediri, Indonesia. PT Gudang Garam Tbk is a subsidiary of PT Suryaduta Investama.
